description:
Do people who reject God end up burning forever in hell? The Bible does not talk about everlasting hell for sinners. Reading the Bible in context is important. Sinners are destroyed in the end. But this is simply an end to evil, not a continual, burning hell where anyone is tormented. It is rather destruction that lasts forever.

Blog: https://www.ibelievebible.com/the-final-judgment/
